Description:
    Wires the app for collaborative documents: a DocumentChannel speaking
    the y-websocket protocol over the gem-owned document storage
    (Y::Document + Y::DocumentUpdate — an update log with compaction),
    and the storage migration.

Example:
    bin/rails generate yrby:install

    This will create:
        app/channels/document_channel.rb
        db/migrate/XXXXXXXX_create_yrby_tables.rb
